{"tid":2251350,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工俾人炒左好唔開心","createTime":"2020-10-20T17:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T08:48:58.000Z","uid":213170,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a087a89d14903707c26a942dd96f7aa27ee5662f","tid":2251350,"uid":213170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:43:06.000Z","msg":"前排返新工 雖然唔係自己想返個啲 甚至有少少抗拒 但最尾都決定咗繼續做<br />\n先天條件不足 俾心機同盡左力去做 但老細好似點都唔滿意咁 最尾仲俾人炒左 <br />\n而家反省完自己但都keep住唔開心 好似喺無底深潭咁"},{"pid":"9b79380d973e84b4df56bae85f0603d57d55e53b","tid":2251350,"uid":38904,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:45:01.000Z","msg":"唔需要因為一份工嘅performance而失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269da4d6db1a5bc4ce5cd430b617ab1c05bed4ad","tid":2251350,"uid":43441,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"a087a89d14903707c26a942dd96f7aa27ee5662f","tid":2251350,"uid":213170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:43:06.000Z","msg":"前排返新工 雖然唔係自己想返個啲 甚至有少少抗拒 但最尾都決定咗繼續做<br />\n先天條件不足 俾心機同盡左力去做 但老細好似點都唔滿意咁 最尾仲俾人炒左 <br />\n而家反省完自己但都keep住唔開心 好似喺無底深潭咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:45:55.000Z","msg":"一份工唔如意並唔代表份份都會咁，人夾人緣，加油"},{"pid":"31f44fb4842c5662add858d97cdc240f35aef04d","tid":2251350,"uid":201414,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:48:11.000Z","msg":"屌 呢啲工番唔番都擺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c353482e3411e8fb5faf5e9bab8c344435a3403","tid":2251350,"uid":7363,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:52:47.000Z","msg":"以前都返過份垃圾工俾人兜咗<br />\n<br />\n不過都好快振作返 所以唔使咁快灰心<br />\n<br />\n樓主加油 相信自己嘅能力 一定會搵到份更好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75aa914d81e7d0f4be58338cde93290e5c99835d","tid":2251350,"uid":161541,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:57:26.000Z","msg